name: Sculptor
tagline: Allows you to easily 'sculpt' beautiful, cross-browser HTML dropdowns with standard CSS
body:
### Welcome to Sculptor JS
Sculptor JS is a very quick and easy way for you to create fully styled and beautiful, cross-browser compliant drop-downs. This site will be updated with full usage information and examples but in the meantime, please read the comprehensive [README](https://github.com/ordergroove/sculptorjs/blob/master/README.md)
